headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Ulta Beauty (ULTA) After Its Strong One Year Share Price Run
summary: If you are wondering whether Ulta Beauty's share price still offers value after a strong run, this article will walk through what the current market price might be implying. Ulta Beauty recently closed at US$684.79, with returns of 0.3% over 7 days, 7.3% over 30 days, 10.4% year to date, 86.9% over 1 year, 31.2% over 3 years, and 105.4% over 5 years.
